description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 210, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 5 for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30703-55611-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [210 Votes, Top 5% Score]
